cancer that affects plasma cells they
accumulate in the bone marrow crowding
out the normal plasma cells that help
fight infection this foundation's model
is to use precision medicine which helps
every patient get the right amount of
treatment based on their specific
information it's built on three pillars
the data bank which generates and
aggregates vital information about the
disease patients and treatment the
Learning Network which takes world
leading scientists to utilize that
information to guide their research and
the clinic which takes the information
and feeds it back to the data bank
improving the precision of treatment
